The animation is lagging because you're animating layout properties (width, left, margin) which trigger CPU-bound reflows. To achieve 60fps GPU acceleration:

Current (slow):
.card { transition: left 0.3s, width 0.3s; }

Optimized (fast):
.card { transition: transform 0.3s, opacity 0.3s; will-change: transform; }

Use transform: translateX() instead of left, and transform: scaleX() instead of width. This moves compositing to the GPU and avoids layout recalculations.
